<div id="main">

	<div id="img">
		<img src="images/Latex-6507.jpg" />
		<p>Learn how to typeset math nicely... Find material about <a href="/latex">LaTeX course and training</a>.</p>
	</div>

	<h2>What is UCLouvain<br />ACM Student Chapter?</h2>

	<p>The UCLouvain ACM Student Chapter is an affiliated association
	to the Association for Computing Machinery (ACM). It primarily aims
	promoting computer science among both students and professionals.
	The association organizes events, tutorials, programming
	contests... Its activities are open to every interested people.</p>
	
	<div class="grey-box">
		<form action="/services/subscribe" method="post" enctype="multipart/form-data" id="subscribe-form">
			<label for="mail">Subscribe<br /> to the newsletter</label>
			<input type="text" value="john.doe@mail.com" name="mail" id="mail"/>
			<input type="submit" value="Go Â»" />
			<p id="message" ></p>
		</form>
	</div>
	
	<script type="text/javascript">
		$(document).ready(function() {
			form = "form#subscribe-form";
			$(form).submit(function() {
				$.ajax({type: "POST", url: $(form).attr('action'), data: $(form).serialize(), dataType: "json",
					error: function(data) {
						if (data.status == 500) {
							$('form#subscribe-form input').hide();
							$('p#message').show();
							$('p#message').html("A server error occured, please retry later.");
						}
					},
					success: function(data) {
						$('p#message').show();
						if (data == "invalid_email") {
							$('p#message').html("Your e-mail is not valid.");
						} else if (data == "missing_email") {
							$('p#message').html("Your e-mail is missing.");
						} else {
							$('form#subscribe-form input').hide();
							$('p#message').html("You are now subscribed.");
						}
					}});
				return false;
			});
		});
	</script>

</div>
